text = "“Originating from Rajasthan,
Mawa Kachori is like a royal sweet surprise in a crispy shell.

Its golden crust hides a rich filling of mawa and nuts,
soaked in sugar syrup that melts in every bite.

It’s not just a dessert but a festive celebration,
a piece of tradition passed down for generations!”"

